            <qualityControl>
                <description>
                    <para>The majority of the records were created by R.H. Wardell and are generally of a good standard. The vascular plant records have all been through BSBI verification. The rest have been assessed by LERC staff and have been passed to the relevant county recorder/national scheme for verification and will be updated once these assessments have been made available. The computerisation of these records has been subject to validation.  The spatial reference (grid reference) has been validated.</para>
